  <article class="article">

    <div class="experience-callout" style="border-left: 4px solid var(--c-accent, #2563eb); background: var(--c-surface, #f8fafc); padding: 1rem 1.25rem; margin: 1.5rem 0; border-radius: 0 6px 6px 0; font-size: 0.95rem;">
      <strong>First-hand note:</strong> PrivacyComply runs on <strong>iubenda</strong> — the cookie banner you see in the bottom corner of this page, the privacy policy at <a href="/privacy-policy.html">/privacy-policy.html</a>, the cookie policy, and the terms-and-conditions are all generated and hosted by iubenda. So while we cover Termly and Osano based on vendor documentation and verified-user reviews, the iubenda assessment in this article reflects what we actually use day-to-day on this site. Specifics from running iubenda live: the cookie banner widget loads from <code>embeds.iubenda.com</code> as a single script tag, the Consent Database logs every accept/reject event with a timestamp you can query later for proof-of-consent, and the privacy policy is a hosted page on iubenda.com that you link to rather than copy-paste, which means regulatory changes propagate without a redeploy on your end.
    </div>

    <div class="tldr">
      <strong>Bottom line:</strong> iubenda offers the broadest feature set under one subscription — cookie consent, legal documents, accessibility tools, and whistleblowing management. Termly positions itself as an affordable all-in-one solution for small businesses. Osano emphasizes enterprise-grade privacy management with regulatory guarantees. Pricing starts at €4.99/month (iubenda), ~$10/month (Termly), and $199/month (Osano).
    </div>

    <p>Choosing between iubenda, Termly, and Osano means weighing different approaches to <a href="/what-is-gdpr.html">privacy compliance</a>. Each platform handles <a href="/best-cookie-consent-tools-2026.html">cookie consent</a> banners and privacy documentation, but they differ in scope, pricing transparency, and how they support businesses of varying sizes.</p>

    <h2>Where each tool wins (honest verdict)</h2>
    <p>If you only have 30 seconds, here is the single sentence answer for each platform — then the rest of this guide walks through how we got there.</p>

