            <td class="tool-name">iubenda</td>
            <td>One subscription that covers cookie banner + privacy policy + cookie policy + terms + DSAR + ROPA, multi-jurisdiction (EU + UK + Brazil + Canada + California), and a Google-certified CMP for AdSense / Ads / Analytics.</td>
            <td>You're a US-only small business that only needs a free cookie banner and a basic privacy policy — you'd be overpaying for documents you don't use.</td>
          </tr>
