            <td class="tool-name">Termly</td>
            <td>The cheapest functional free tier in the category for a US-focused site, the easiest no-code setup, and CCPA/CPRA-first documents.</td>
            <td>You ship into the EU/UK and need an IAB-validated CMP on the free plan, or you operate in more than 2–3 jurisdictions — international coverage gets thin fast.</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
