    <h3>Key Takeaways</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>iubenda provides the widest compliance scope with cookie consent, legal documents, accessibility, and DSAR tools in one subscription</li>
      <li>Termly serves small businesses seeking affordable all-in-one compliance, while Osano focuses on enterprise privacy management with regulatory guarantees</li>
      <li>Pricing transparency varies significantly, with iubenda and Termly publishing clear plans and Osano requiring custom quotes for most tiers</li>
